profile:
We offer cleaning services for commercial, residential, Airbnb, post construction, post renovations, move-in and move-out cleans. Commercial buildings, schools, churches, medical facilities, office buildings, and more. 
Some of our services include: Dusting, sweeping, vacuuming and mopping floors, windows, furniture, equipment and appliances. Depending on the job description additional tasks may include removing rubbish, documenting routine inspections and carrying out basic maintenance.
We customize our services to meet your specific needs. 
We provide our services in Hamilton, Burlington, Niagara Falls, St Catharines, Grimsby, Stoney Creek, Brantford, Oakville, Mississauga, Toronto, Guelph, Kitchener, Cambridge. 
We promise quality, reliable cleaning service every time so our loyal customers feel special. We work hard to be the best. Our products are high-quality and safe. And we focus on the details so you are always left satisfied.

Ask us about daily, weekly and bi-weekly weekly service. Contracts welcome. 
Our reputation is spotless!
Call: 1-833-FLORES-3
E-mail: info@floresclean.com .  

Visit us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/florescleaningservices
and Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/florescleaningservices
